In this 3D effects on graphs also
decreases the Data-Ink Ratio.

21
00:01:05.570 --> 00:01:08.670
Typically, it's 3D effects makes
really in a graph more difficult.

22
00:01:09.690 --> 00:01:12.970
The third dimension in the graph does not
exist in the original data that makes

23
00:01:12.970 --> 00:01:14.860
