because it stores a graph.

27
00:01:26.310 --> 00:01:29.620
Our 3D perception is quite limited
compared to our 2D perception.

28
00:01:30.660 --> 00:01:34.670
In 3D, the size of the bar
depends on how far it is from us.

29
00:01:34.670 --> 00:01:38.090
